# TASK_PACKET

Task ID
CRUSHR-HARDEN-03B

Title
Salvage schema reconciliation and emitted-output contract repair

Role
BUILDER

Objective
Reconcile `crushr-salvage` emitted classifications, provenance, and report surfaces with the active salvage schemas so that machine-readable outputs become trustworthy again.

This packet exists because schema drift now undermines confidence in the research artifacts. If emitted salvage outputs do not match the documented schema vocabulary and semantics, downstream summaries, comparisons, and whitepaper evidence are not trustworthy.

This is a contract-repair packet.
It is not a format-redesign packet.

