---------------------------------------------------------------------

Acceptance criteria

This packet is acceptable only if all of the following are true:

1. Salvage emitted output conforms to the active schema.
2. Classification/provenance/reason vocabularies are truthful and aligned.
3. Any material semantic change is versioned correctly.
4. Tests prove schema conformance.
5. Docs/examples match actual emitted behavior.
6. Downstream consumers can trust salvage outputs again.
